data.description: Charming Renovated Home with Farmhouse details. Spacious Living Room/Dining Room layout features a painted wainscoting, durable laminate flooring & plentiful natural light. Large Kitchen offers NEW Stainless Steel LG appliances, shiplap inspired decor, large pantry/utility room, & access to the rear deck and fully fenced back yard. Main level Master Bedroom features a faux coffered ceiling, and closet with built-in organizers. Main level Full Bath with corner, step-in shower has been remodeled with conveniently located laundry area. Upper level offers Two Bedrooms with new carpet and second Full Bathroom with a gorgeous soaker tub with designer faucet hardware. NEW Roof, Furnace, A/C, Windows, and plumbing-all with transferable warranties!
